reviewText: The songs are just beautiful in this movie!!
Shammi's excellent acting as always.  Great movie.
PLAYED BY EVERGREEN HERO SHAMMI OF KAPOOR'S FAMILY AND CO STARRED BY KALPANA ANOTHER BEAUTY OF INDIAN SCREEN. OUTDOOR SCENES WITH SONGS ARE QUITE ENTERTAINING. FAMILY DRAMA  AS WITH JANWAR.

Indian Movie - Professor received as ordered. Shammi Kapoor inacted and accomodated for old professor as available position was only for old age person. Movie seemed to be of North Indian Village. Enjoyed.
